      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 📄 CV-to-Job Matcher v2 (PDF Upload)\n\nUpload your CV as a PDF + paste a job description\n→ Gemini extracts your CV text automatically\n→ analyzes your fit → emails you a full report.\n\nUpgrade of Workflow 03 — no more copy-pasting!\n\nAuthor: Slim Khardani\nGitHub: github.com/slimkhardani",
