    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⚙️ Setup Required\n\n1. Gemini API Key\n   → aistudio.google.com\n   → Free tier is enough\n\n2. Gmail OAuth2\n   → Connect your Google account\n   → Allow n8n permissions\n\nNo manual CV text needed!\nPDF is extracted automatically.",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 368,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -96,
        192
      ],
      "id": "b2e590bb-c56f-4641-a2ab-a63f68401927",
      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔄 Workflow Steps\n\n1. WEBHOOK TRIGGER\n   Receives multipart POST with:\n   - CV as PDF file (field: data)\n   - jobTitle, company, jobDescription\n\n2. EXTRACT FROM FILE\n   Extracts raw text from the PDF\n   automatically — no copy-paste needed\n\n3. GEMINI AI\n   Analyzes CV vs job description:\n   - Match Score (X/10)\n   - Top 3 matching skills\n   - Top 3 skill gaps\n   - Cover email opener\n\n4. GMAIL\n   Sends full report to your inbox",
        "height": 480,
        "width": 352,
        "color": 5
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -496,
        -208
      ],
      "id": "e6457a04-f162-4890-b947-b5532628ee5c",
      "name": "Sticky Note2"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🚀 How to Use\n\ncurl -X POST YOUR_WEBHOOK_URL \\\n-F \"data=@/path/to/your/CV.pdf\" \\\n-F \"jobTitle=Backend Intern\" \\\n-F \"company=Activepieces\" \\\n-F \"jobDescription=Looking for Node.js,\n    NestJS and Docker experience...\"\n\nCheck your inbox for the full\nmatch report from Gemini!",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 368,
